{
  "stem": "3097.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a lot of partisans from before who were anti-Communists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And even the Polish, the-- the people who were from the London government, with Mikolaj and so forth, you see, were against the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there was a lot yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a-- was like a civil war at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The regime didn't set in yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So the people started to aggregate by this building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they started to some-- agitate that those Jews there, you see, they are rich, and they are supported, and they take care of this [? way ?] of the children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they started to attack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They even involved the members of the militia, of the people who were supposed to defend them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when they tried to intervene, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Kahana, who was the president of the organization there, went, tried to intervene, and tried to get the-- the bishop of Kielce to intervene.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He couldn't accomplish anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He didn't want to have a part of it because, you know, they were against the Communists, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "See, there was still an antagonistic way of doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened, finally, when they brought the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the fire department to disperse the people with fire-- with the water hoses, they cut the hoses, the people, and just broke the door in.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they start to-- the mob got in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They started to throw out the people through the windows, kill them with any form of-- of-- you know, with sticks and-- and axes and any kind of implementation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they killed a lot of-- even a woman with a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they ask-- I have the court proceedings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The asked the man, why did you kill the child?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
